      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Chop your <strong>waxy potatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Trim, then chop your <strong>green beans</strong> in half</p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach </strong>and pat dry with kitchen paper</p>",
