    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pat your <strong>haddock bites </strong>dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Tip: Unevenly sized haddock bites? Chop any larger ones into bite-sized pieces!</p><p>Add your <strong>cornflour </strong>to a medium sized bowl with your <strong>ground turmeric</strong>, <strong>half </strong>your <strong>curry powder </strong>(you’ll use the rest later!) and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>haddock bites</strong> to the bowl and give everything a good mix up until the haddock bites are fully coated</p>",
      "order": 5,
