    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes are cooked, add the <strong>cooked green beans </strong>and <strong>nigella seeds</strong> with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>warm potato salad</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>mayo </strong>and <strong>remaining curry powder </strong>in a small bowl – this is your <strong>curried mayo</strong></p>",
